and simple reconstruction like an {\color{green}orthonormal basis}.
    
\medskip

{\color{ZurichBlue} Discrete wavelets:}
Can one construct a {\color{green}discrete wavelet system}
\begin{align*}
 W(\psi) = \{ \psi_{j,m} = 2^{j}\psi(2^{j}x - m): (j,m) \in \Lambda\},
\end{align*}
where $\Lambda \subset \R^2$ is a lattice and $W(\psi)$ is an orthonormal basis?
\begin{align*}
 f = \sum_{(j,m) \in \Lambda} \langle f,\psi_{j,m} \rangle \psi_{j,m}.
\end{align*}


