\begin{frame}{Tools for Applications}
 
Let $\psi \in L^2(\R)$ be a wavelet and $\phi\in L^2(\R)$ the corresponding scaling function such that 
$$
\{\phi(\cdot - m): m\in \Z\} \cup \{\psi_{j,m} := 2^{j/2}\psi(2^{j} \cdot - m): j\geq 0, m\in \Z\}
$$
is an ONB for $L^2(\R)$. \qquad 
